The '''Thermal Detonator Launcher''' allowed the user to shoot [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonators]] when attached to the bottom of a [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]]. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] mercenary [[Rianna Saren]] used this attachment with her blaster pistol.

